    ChatZoneExitedEvent

    public class ZoneExitedEvent
extends ContextualEvent<Zone>
    Defines a ZoneExitEvent. Zone exit events are fired when an entity has left a Zone. This event extends ContextualEvent; as such, the context for this event is the zone that the entity exited.
